COVID-19 Status 💉 🦠

As of 12:54PM PT today, over 1.4 million Canadians have tested positive for COVID-19. Sadly, 26.6 thousand have died.

In the last day, 531 new infections were reported and 6 deaths. This is trending upwards.

Fortunately, 49.3 million doses of the vaccine have been administered. For those 12 years and older, 81.1% have their 1st shot and 66.8% are fully vaccinated!

Vaccination is speeding up, but there are 10.4 million doses in the freezer. It currently takes ~34 days for new deliveries to get into arms. At the current rate, all Canadians aged 12+ will have the first dose by 2022-Jan-02 and fully vaccinated by 2022-Jan-30. There is no approved vaccine for children aged 11 or younger.
